title: Couple With Heart: Man, Man, Medium Skin Tone, Medium-Dark Skin Tone
description: Represents a romantic couple composed of two men, with specified skin tones. It conveys love, partnership, and affection between two men.
apple_vendor_description: This heartwarming emoji on Apple devices portrays two men with medium and medium-dark skin tones, their figures rendered with the smooth, realistic lighting and soft rounded edges typical of Apple's design language. Nestled between them is a radiant heart, its gradient softly pulsing with affection, signifying love and partnership. The emoji on Apple devices beautifully captures the essence of a strong, loving bond between two men.
